{"id":10208,"date":"2025-12-15T07:10:25","date_gmt":"2025-12-15T07:10:25","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.giridhareye.org\/?p=10208"},"modified":"2026-02-23T05:53:59","modified_gmt":"2026-02-23T05:53:59","slug":"dr_sneha_giridhar","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.giridhareye.org\/dr_sneha_giridhar\/","title":{"rendered":"Dr. Sneha Giridhar"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><div class=\"fusion-fullwidth fullwidth-box fusion-builder-row-1 fusion-flex-container has-pattern-background has-mask-background nonhundred-percent-fullwidth non-hundred-percent-height-scrolling\" style=\"--awb-border-radius-top-left:0px;--awb-border-radius-top-right:0px;--awb-border-radius-bottom-right:0px;--awb-border-radius-bottom-left:0px;--awb-flex-wrap:wrap;\" ><div class=\"fusion-builder-row fusion-row fusion-flex-align-items-flex-start fusion-flex-content-wrap\" style=\"max-width:1414.4px;margin-left: calc(-4% \/ 2 );margin-right: calc(-4% \/ 2 );\"><div class=\"fusion-layout-column fusion_builder_column fusion-builder-column-0 fusion_builder_column_1_1 1_1 fusion-flex-column\" style=\"--awb-padding-top:40px;--awb-padding-bottom:50px;--awb-bg-size:cover;--awb-width-large:100%;--awb-margin-top-large:0px;--awb-spacing-right-large:1.92%;--awb-margin-bottom-large:20px;--awb-spacing-left-large:1.92%;--awb-width-medium:100%;--awb-order-medium:0;--awb-spacing-right-medium:1.92%;--awb-spacing-left-medium:1.92%;--awb-width-small:100%;--awb-order-small:0;--awb-spacing-right-small:1.92%;--awb-spacing-left-small:1.92%;\"><div class=\"fusion-column-wrapper fusion-column-has-shadow fusion-flex-justify-content-flex-start fusion-content-layout-column\"><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-1 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-three\" style=\"--awb-margin-bottom:0px;\"><h3 class=\"fusion-title-heading title-heading-left\" style=\"margin:0;\"><\/h3><\/div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-1\"><\/div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-2\"><\/div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-3\"><\/div><div class=\"fusion-title title fusion-title-2 fusion-sep-none fusion-title-text fusion-title-size-three\" style=\"--awb-margin-top:40px;--awb-margin-bottom:0px;\"><h3 class=\"fusion-title-heading title-heading-left\" style=\"margin:0;\">Educational Qualifications<\/p>\n<div><span data-fusion-font=\"true\" style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><\/p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 40px;\">MBBS, Amrita Institute of Medical Sciences, Kochi<\/p>\n<p><\/span><span data-fusion-font=\"true\" style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><\/p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 40px;\">Diploma in Ophthalmology (DO), Aravind Eye Care System, Madurai<\/p>\n<p><\/span><span data-fusion-font=\"true\" style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><\/p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 40px;\">Diplomate of National Board in Ophthalmology (DNB), Aravind Eye Care System, Tirunelveli<\/p>\n<p><\/span><\/p>\n<div>\n<p><\/p>\n<p><span data-fusion-font=\"true\" style=\"font-size: 40px;\">Specialisation<\/span><\/div>\n<div>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 20px; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"><\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 40px;\"><\/p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 40px;\">International Clinical Fellowship in Medical Retina, Uveitis and Genetics, Moorfields Eye Hospital NHS Foundation Trust, London (2023\u20132025.<\/p>\n<\/p>\n<p><span data-fusion-font=\"true\" style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><\/p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 40px;\">Two-year Fellowship in Vitreous and Retina, Sankara Nethralaya, Chennai (2020\u20132022).<\/p>\n<p><\/span><\/div>\n<div>\n<p><\/p>\n<p><span data-fusion-font=\"true\" style=\"font-size: 40px;\">Work Experience<\/span><br \/><span data-fusion-font=\"true\" style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><\/p>\n<ul><\/ul>\n<p><\/span><br \/><span data-fusion-font=\"true\" style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"><\/p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 40px;\">Clinical Fellow, Medical Retina, Uveitis and Genetics, Moorfields Eye Hospital, London (Jan 2023\u2013Jul 2025), including independent and locum consultant-level clinics, virtual medical retina services, and Retinal Advice and Refer (RAR) pathway.<\/p>\n<p><\/span><br \/><span style=\"background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"><\/p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 40px;\">Vitreoretinal Fellow, Sankara Nethralaya, Chennai (Research Fellowship 2019\u20132020; VR Fellowship 2020\u20132022) with significant surgical exposure in pars plana vitrectomy, scleral buckling, membrane peeling and complex retinal detachment repair.<\/p>\n<p><\/span><br \/><span style=\"background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"><\/p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 40px;\">Postgraduate resident, Aravind Eye Hospital, with around 600 independent cataract surgeries and participation in cataract and diabetic retinopathy screening camps.<\/p>\n<p><\/span><\/span><\/div>\n<div>\n<p><\/p>\n<p><span data-fusion-font=\"true\" style=\"font-size: 40px;\">Publications<\/span><\/div>\n<div>\n<p><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 20px; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"><\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 40px;\">Sen P, Giridhar S. Commentary: Retinal folds: To operate or not to operate. Indian Journal of Ophthalmology. 2020 Jun 1;68(6):1200.<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 20px; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"><\/p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 40px;\">Das T, Agarwal M, Behera U, Bhattacharjee H, Bhende M, Das AV, Dave VP, Dogra A, Ghosh AK, Giridhar S, Joseph J. Diagnosis and management of fungal endophthalmitis: Indian perspective. Expert Review of Ophthalmology. 2020 Nov 1;15(6):355-65.<\/p>\n<p><\/span><br \/><span style=\"font-size: 20px; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"><\/p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 40px;\">Shah A, Giridhar S, Patnaik G, Mhatre R, Das D, Janani MK, Mahadevan A, Biswas J. Histopathological, Immunohistochemical and Molecular Biologic Study of an Enucleated Specimen of a Case of Eales\u2019 Disease.<\/p>\n<p><\/span><br \/><span style=\"font-size: 20px; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"><\/p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 40px;\">Sneha Giridhar, Lalit Verma, Anand Rajendran, Muna Bhende, Mallika Goyal, Kim Ramasamy, Rajalakshmi, Padmaja R, Sundaram Natarajan, Mahesh Shanmugam Palanivelu Rajiv Raman, Sobha Sivaprasad, Diabetic macular edema treatment guidelines in India: All India Ophthalmological Society diabetic retinopathy task force, Vitreoretinal Society of India Consensus Statement.<\/p>\n<p><\/span><br \/><span style=\"font-size: 20px; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"><\/p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 40px;\">Ratra D, Roy K, Giridhar S, Madaan S. Comparison Between Ranibizumab Biosimilar, Innovator Ranibizumab and Bevacizumab in a Real World Situation.<\/p>\n<p><\/span><br \/><span style=\"font-size: 20px; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"><\/p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 40px;\">Ratra D, Chattree S, Raviselvan M, Pradhan A, Giridhar S. Structural and functional phenotypic features and molecular analysis of Indian patients with Bietti crystalline dystrophy. Indian Journal of Ophthalmology.<\/p>\n<p><\/span><br \/><span style=\"font-size: 20px; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"><\/p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 40px;\">Azzopardi M, Giridhar S, Tsika C, Koutsocheras G, Katzakis M, Demir B, Rahman W, Heng LZ, Chong YJ, Logeswaran A. A Comparison of Ultra-Widefield Imaging Quality Obtained with Zeiss Clarus and Optos for Virtual Medical Retina Services. Journal of Clinical Medicine. 2025 May 8;14(10):3270.<\/p>\n<p><\/span><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<div>\n<p><span style=\"background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"><br \/><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); font-size: 40px;\" data-fusion-font=\"true\">Achievements<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span data-fusion-font=\"true\" style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><\/p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 40px;\"><\/p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 40px;\">Swarnalatha Punshi Award for Best Research Fellow, Medical Research Foundation, Sankara Nethralaya (2021).<\/p>\n<p><\/span><span data-fusion-font=\"true\" style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><\/p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 40px;\">Presenting author for papers and posters at major meetings, including AIOS, EURETINA, USI, TNOA and Moorfields courses and symposia.<\/p>\n<p><\/span><span data-fusion-font=\"true\" style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><\/p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 40px;\">Active involvement in clinical audits and quality improvement projects at Moorfields Eye Hospital, including studies on peripapillary polypoidal vasculopathy and virtual medical retina clinic outcomes.<\/p>\n<p><\/span><\/div>\n<div>\n<p><span style=\"background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"><br \/><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); font-size: 40px;\" data-fusion-font=\"true\">Book Chapters<\/span><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<div>\n<p><\/p>\n<p><span data-fusion-font=\"true\" style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><\/p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 40px;\">Sneha Giridhar, Dipankar Das, Jyotirmay Biswas. Intraocular Tumours\u2014Advances in Ophthalmic Pathology. Advances in Ophthalmology and Optometry.June 2021<\/p>\n<p><\/span><span data-fusion-font=\"true\" style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><\/p>\n<p style=\"padding-left: 40px;\">Vikas Khetan, Arkaprava Pradhan, Sneha Giridhar. Multimodal imaging of intraocular tumours.Fingers Essential Ophthalmic Oncology.2024 <\/p>\n<p><\/span><\/p><\/div>\n<\/div><\/h3><\/div><div class=\"fusion-text fusion-text-4\"><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><div class=\"fusion-fullwidth fullwidth-box fusion-builder-row-2 fusion-flex-container nonhundred-percent-fullwidth non-hundred-percent-height-scrolling fusion-animated\" style=\"--awb-background-position:right center;--awb-border-sizes-top:0px;--awb-border-sizes-bottom:0px;--awb-border-sizes-left:0px;--awb-border-sizes-right:0px;--awb-border-radius-top-left:0px;--awb-border-radius-top-right:0px;--awb-border-radius-bottom-right:0px;--awb-border-radius-bottom-left:0px;--awb-padding-top:0px;--awb-padding-right:30px;--awb-padding-bottom:65px;--awb-padding-left:30px;--awb-padding-top-small:125.863px;--awb-m